      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Balint Pfliegel</b>\n</p><p><b>Bálint Pfliegel</b>,<br />\na Hungarian computer scientist with a M.Sc. in CS from the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Budapest_University_of_Technology_and_Economics\">Budapest University of Technology</a> in 1999 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe is author of <a href=\"/Portfish\" title=\"Portfish\">Portfish</a>, a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.NET_Framework\">.Net</a> port of <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> written in <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Balint_Pfliegel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42894&amp;start=31\">Re: Stockfish port to C# Complete</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Balint Pfliegel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 21, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43571\">Portfish - C# port of Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Balint Pfliegel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44114\">[.Net only</a> - fast bit operations] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Balint Pfliegel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45388&amp;start=6\">Re: Question About CPP-C#, Performance, and Square Representation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Balint Pfliegel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 30, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50498\">UCI variants support</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Balint Pfliegel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2013</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Balint_Pfliegel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/b%C3%A1lint-pfliegel-b522922/\">Bálint Pfliegel | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/bpfliegel\">bpfliegel · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Balint_Pfliegel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/b%C3%A1lint-pfliegel-b522922/\">Bálint Pfliegel | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43571\">Portfish - C# port of Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Balint Pfliegel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2012</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301063425\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.005 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 43/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 98/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7227-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301063425 and revision id 19688\n -->\n"
